Revision history for Pid-File-Flock

0.08    2010-11-19
        Switched to Module::Install

0.07    2010-11-08
        Fixed bugs under MSWin32.

0.06    2010-10-28
        New option ('raise') implemented.
        Intended for usage from eval block.
        Thanks to Jozef Kutej and Vladimir Timofeev.

0.05    2010-10-07
        Fixed potential race condition.
        Thanks to Jozef Kutej.

0.04    2010-07-13
        Added 'abandon' method special for using
        in forking applications.

0.03    2009-04-21
        Explicitly die in Makefile.PL under cygwin.

0.02    2009-04-15
        POSIX compliance file locking semantic

0.01    2009-04-13
        Source imported

